    "title": "生徒会長の思い",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、買い出しの途中――",
            "enText": "One day, while out shopping…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "pathId": -2085885211253068285,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "うん。\r\nこれでひとつ解決だ。",
            "enText": "Yes. That's one solution.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -896179320922072913
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6813550755617330864
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8995347091229172798,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフが\r\n近くの店舗から出てきたので声をかけてみた。",
            "enText": "Symboli Rudolf came out of a nearby \nshop and I called out to her.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 1574135933167535222
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 7547098701078933128
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1270542760035786381,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "やあ、奇遇だね。\r\n買い出しか何かかな。",
            "enText": "Hi, how are you? I wonder if you're \nshopping or something.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": 1385051491192448870
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6085868991751712519
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -45883195257413222,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "私はちょうどタオルの発注を終えて、\r\n次に向かうところだ。",
            "enText": "I've just finished ordering the towels and \nam on my way to the next one.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "タオル？",
                    "enText": "Towels?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 185,
                    "pathId": -8927174382811721213
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 4966029607222736022
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8632927270789500135,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ああ。生徒会で準備している\r\n貸し出し用を増やしておこうと思ってね。",
            "enText": "Oh. I thought I'd increase the number of \nloaners we have in the student council.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": -4050820674068482164
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 881401562893039161
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5779518019816498182,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "来週は荒天が続く予報だ。借りに来る子も\r\n増えるだろう。それに備える必要がある。",
            "enText": "The weather is forecast to be stormy next \nweek. There will be more children coming to \nborrow. We need to be prepared for this.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": 1815515963514050835
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6597656562792112746
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2448489237738990169,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "このあと傘等の雨具の発注もすませれば\r\n万全の態勢が整えられる。",
            "enText": "After this, umbrellas and other rain gear \nwill be ordered and we will be ready to go.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ありがとう、おかげで雨の日も安心だ",
                    "enText": "Thanks to you, we're safe from the rain.",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ありがとう、おかげで雨の日も安心だね",
                    "enText": "Thank you, you've made my \nrainy day a lot easier.",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "お疲れ様。学園のために大変そうだ",
                    "enText": "Good work. Looks like a lot \nof work for the school.",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "お疲れ様。学園のために大変そうだね",
                    "enText": "Good work. You're doing a great \njob for the school.",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "trainerGender": "m",
            "animData": [
