                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": -1988203066280313827
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7172632186840272718,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "雨の日に限らず、学園の皆が夢に向かって\r\n一意専心できる環境を、私は作りたいんだ。",
            "enText": "I want to create an environment where \neveryone at the school can focus on their \ndreams, not just on a rainy day.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 6811721929776832368
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": -870714388992581048
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5343471189728066640,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "君も何か要望があれば、\r\n遠慮会釈なく言ってくれ。",
            "enText": "If you have any requests, please \ndon't hesitate to ask.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 140,
                    "pathId": 1155007069566186630
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 1813387963656879085
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6460134733513096376,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "礼には及ばないよ。生徒会の仕事で\r\n街に出る必要があったから、そのついでさ。",
            "enText": "No need to thank me. I had to go into town \non student council business.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": 4152174823224154964
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6549310449813075989
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4523531942210763856,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "それに皆のトレーニング環境向上に\r\n責任がある身だからね。当然のことだ。",
            "enText": "And I'm responsible for improving \nthe training environment for everyone. \nIt's only natural.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -3622380139462916687
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 222934108626919911
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3649416057258942763,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "さて、発注が終わったら、コースの水はけも\r\nチェックしておきたいな……少し急ぐか。",
            "enText": "Now that the order has been placed, I'd like \nto check the drainage of the course… I'm in \na bit of a hurry.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": -6937304162854268832
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 1459735444323840475
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7370052968456432454,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフの\r\n責任感とバイタリティには\n参考にすべき点が多いように感じた。",
            "enText": "I felt that Symboli Rudolf's sense of \nresponsibility and vitality was a good \nexample to follow.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
